import SearchBar from './SearchBar'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const Nav = ({ onSearch }) =>{

    return (
        <nav>
            <SearchBar onSearch={onSearch}/>
            <button>
                <link to='/about' >ABOUT</link>
            </button>

            <button>
                <link to='/home' >HOME</link>
            </button>
        </nav>
    )
}

export default Nav
